high_descs: Go to the diningtable with the microwave on it ahead of you and to the right.
Pick up the tomato.
Turn to the fridge to the right of the table and approach it.
Place the tomato in the fridge.
Turn left towards that table from earlier, then left again and straight towards the black coffee table, standing in between the coffeetable and the couch.
From the perspective between the couch and the table, pick up the tomato on the right.
Return to the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place two Tomato in a Fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, continue to the diningtable, turn left.
Take the tomato.
Turn around. Reach the wall. Turn right until you are in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge door. Place the tomato on the lower level. Close the door.
Leave the room. Turn left, then right and go forward. Turn left until you are between the coffeetable and the sofa. Turn left.
Grab the tomato on the right.
Go back to the fridge.
Open the door. Place the tomato next to the other one, closer to the bottom of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Search for two tomatoes. Place them in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left toward the diningtable with the microwave.
Pick up the tomato on the table.
Turn around, head toward the fridge.
Place the tomato on the shelf in the fridge.
Head toward the microwave and turn left, go to the coffee table in front of the sofa.
Pick up the tomato from the coffee table.
Head back to the fridge.
Open the fridge, Place the tomato behind the other tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place two Tomato in the Fridge.
